{
  "texts": [
    "These advancements enhance data collection and provide real-time feedback, bridging the gap between virtual and physical sensory environments.",
    "The integration of AI with these technologies not only improves the accuracy of flavor analysis but also opens up new opportunities for interdisciplinary collaborations, raising essential ethical considerations for the future of sensory science.",
    "AI's integration with emerging technologies in olfaction and gustation is paving the way for innovative research and applications.",
    "AI not only enhances the precision of aroma and flavor analysis but also synergizes with technologies such as the Internet of Things (IoT), big data analytics, and blockchain to create more efficient systems for food development and monitoring.",
    "Firstly, the application of IoT technology serves as a powerful tool for real-time data collection and analysis from various sensory sensors embedded in production environments (Huang et al. 2024)."
  ]
}